Please, stop writing in capitals an entire message.
Try to make you understood more easy.

As I said, CPU core voltage is on tha last to appear; only iGPU core will come later than it.
Do you get L7700/01 and L7330 voltage?

BTW, why do you expect exactly 1.5V on CPU core?
This voltage is dynamically adjusted.
In fact, it must drop to 0.55V when board boots.
